{"title":"Hexo博客杂项","date":"2020-07-20T07:05:18.547Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 20, 2020","L":"07/20/2020","MM-DD":"07-20"},"author":"秋小日","link":"2020/07/20/Hexo博客杂项","tags":["hexo"],"categories":["hexo"],"updated":"2020-07-20T07:05:18.547Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>本文涉及到的知识点包: 博客一键发布，搜索引擎引擎收录及优化，github和coding站点部署等。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"一.-一键发布\">一. 一键发布<a title=\"#一.-一键发布\" href=\"#一.-一键发布\"></a></h2>\n<p>hexo 框架本身是基于node的，作为一名优秀的node工程师，当然可以添加一行命令，快速发布文章咯。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>项目根目录 -&gt; package.json 文件 -&gt; scripts 参数添加以下命令:</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">\"build\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"git add . &amp;&amp; git commit -m 'update' &amp;&amp; git push origin hexo -f &amp;&amp; hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo d -g\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>hexo 是我编写博客的分支，站点使用的是master分支，只要执行 <code>npm run build</code> 就能一键推送并部署到master分支</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"二.-搜索引擎收录\">二. 搜索引擎收录<a title=\"#二.-搜索引擎收录\" href=\"#二.-搜索引擎收录\"></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"三.-seo优化\">三. SEO优化<a title=\"#三.-seo优化\" href=\"#三.-seo优化\"></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"四.-国内coding部署\">四. 国内coding部署<a title=\"#四.-国内coding部署\" href=\"#四.-国内coding部署\"></a></h2>\n","prev":{"title":"egg-core源码分析","link":"2020/07/20/egg-core源码分析"},"next":{"title":"Docker实战","link":"2020/07/20/Docker实战"},"plink":"http://qiuxiaori.github.com/2020/07/20/Hexo博客杂项/","toc":[{"id":"一.-一键发布","title":"一. 一键发布","index":"1"},{"id":"二.-搜索引擎收录","title":"二. 搜索引擎收录","index":"2"},{"id":"三.-seo优化","title":"三. SEO优化","index":"3"},{"id":"四.-国内coding部署","title":"四. 国内coding部署","index":"4"}],"copyright":{"author":"秋小日","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名（CC BY-NC-ND 4.0)","link":"<a href=\"http://qiuxiaori.github.com/2020/07/20/Hexo博客杂项/\" title=\"Hexo博客杂项\">http://qiuxiaori.github.com/2020/07/20/Hexo博客杂项/</a>"}}